{"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation","title":"Related Documentation"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"],"anchor":"How-to-Guides","title":"How-to Guides","generated":true}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoaddapermanentlicense"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"How to Add a Permanent License","modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"role":"article"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sell a lifetime entitlement alongside a subscription and surface both flags through the paywall plugin."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Many apps offer two ways to buy: a recurring pro subscription and a one-time lifetime purchase. RevenueCat models both as entitlements; "},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" checks each independently and surfaces them as the two flags on "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isPro"},{"type":"text","text":" — active subscription."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" — active lifetime entitlement."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The paywall plugin’s "},{"code":"isGateSatisfied","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"isPro || hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", so feature code keeps a single check while UI can branch on the underlying flags when it needs to."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For the entitlement-mapping rules and edge cases, see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Before-you-start","text":"Before you start"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide assumes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You have completed "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You have configured "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"two","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" entitlements in the RevenueCat dashboard — typically "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pro"},{"type":"text","text":" for the subscription and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lifetime"},{"type":"text","text":" for the one-time purchase. The identifiers are arbitrary; only the strings need to match what you pass into the service."}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-1-Pass-the-second-identifier","text":"Step 1: Pass the second identifier"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Replace the single-entitlement init with the two-arg form:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","","let service = RevenueCatPaywallService(","    entitlementID: \"pro\",","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"",")"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both entitlements are now checked on every "},{"code":"customerInfo()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"customerInfoStream()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" yield, and "},{"code":"restorePurchases()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call. The active state of "},{"code":"pro","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flows into "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the active state of "},{"code":"lifetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flows into "},{"code":"hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The two flags are independent. A user with both active gets both flags set; a user with only one active gets only that flag set."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-2-Wire-the-service-into-the-plugin","text":"Step 2: Wire the service into the plugin"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as the single-entitlement case — the plugin doesn’t need to know about the second identifier:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["plugins.register(","    PaywallPlugin<AppState, AppAction>(","        state: \\.paywall,","        action: AppAction.paywall,","        extractAction: { if case .paywall(let a) = $0 { return a }; return nil },","        service: RevenueCatPaywallService(","            entitlementID: \"pro\",","            permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"","        )","    )",")"]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-3-Decide-whether-feature-code-needs-to-branch","text":"Step 3: Decide whether feature code needs to branch"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For most gated features, keep using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store.paywall.isGateSatisfied"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["if store.paywall.isGateSatisfied { … }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This stays correct whether the user has a subscription or a lifetime license, and works identically in apps that don’t sell a lifetime SKU."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Step-4-Branch-in-UI-when-copy-must-differ","text":"Step 4: Branch in UI when copy must differ"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the paywall sheet should be hidden for lifetime customers (so they’re not pestered to subscribe), or if the customer-center entry should be relabeled, branch on the underlying flag:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["if store.paywall.hasPermanentLicense {","    Text(\"Lifetime member — thank you!\")","} else if store.paywall.isPro {","    Button(\"Manage Subscription\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.presentCustomerCenter))","    }","} else {","    Button(\"Upgrade\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"upgrade-prompt\")))","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lifetime users typically have nothing to manage in App Store \/ Settings. Hiding the customer-center button for them avoids dead-end taps."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"When-to-skip-the-second-identifier","text":"When to skip the second identifier"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" (or omit the parameter) if your app has no lifetime SKU:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["RevenueCatPaywallService(entitlementID: \"pro\")"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" then stays "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":" regardless of any entitlements RevenueCat reports — even if the dashboard accidentally has a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lifetime"},{"type":"text","text":" entitlement that the service is not configured to check. See the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lifetime entitlement is ignored when no permanent-license ID is configured"}]},{"type":"text","text":" test case for the precise behavior."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/EntitlementMapping":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/entitlementmapping","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How RevenueCat’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerInfo.entitlements"},{"type":"text","text":" translates to Swidux’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","role":"article","title":"Entitlement Mapping"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"text":". Implements ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"text":" against ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" for drop-in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterView"},{"text":" presentation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","role":"collection","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToImplementService":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Wire ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" into the ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" plugin so the store sees real-time entitlement updates from RevenueCat.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoimplementservice","role":"article","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","title":"How to Implement the Service"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPresentTheUI":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopresenttheui","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Attach ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallSheet"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterSheet"},{"type":"text","text":" from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"type":"text","text":" to a root view, driven by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallState"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","role":"article","title":"How to Present the UI"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPreviewAndTest":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopreviewandtest","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Drive entitlement state from SwiftUI previews and tests with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" — no RevenueCat SDK call required."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest","role":"article","title":"How to Preview and Test"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/ServiceReference":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"API reference for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" — the RevenueCat-backed ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes.","type":"text"}],"role":"article","title":"Service Reference"}}}